  4. Transform predictors

  6. Stepwise-selection with BIC

Final Model

\[ \begin{align*} \frac{1}{\sqrt{\texttt{PriceinUK}}} &= \beta_0 \\ &+ \beta_1 \ln \texttt{Range} \\ &+ \beta_2 \texttt{TopSpeed} \\ &+ \beta_3 \texttt{TopSpeed}^2 \\ &+ \beta_4 \texttt{Efficiency} \\ &+ \beta_5 \texttt{Efficiency}^2 \\ &+ \epsilon \end{align*} \]
